NOTABLE ACTIVITIES
• Rendering advice and second opinions on individual and corporate income tax and tax treaty issues;
• Strategy consulting in respect of the compatibility of the Polish tax law with EU law and tax treaties;
• Providing training on the issues regarding the concept of beneficial owner (BO), withholding tax (WHT), general anti-avoidance rule (GAAR), principal purposes test (PPT) and the general anti-abuse principle (GAAP) as developed by the Court of Justice of the European Union (CJEU).
